metadata.name: JE VOUDRAIS QUE LE MÉTAVERSE…
metadata.collection: Indigo X hieroglyphica x Ana María Caballero
metadata.description:
JE VOUDRAIS QUE LE MÉTAVERSE explores language's ambiguity through the lens of one sentence with infinite nuanced meanings.

This work is a special edition of hieroglyphica + Ana María Caballero’s fxhash collection I WISH FOR THE METAVERSE. Collectors receive a generative version.
